#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first step involves selecting an institution for the account. If this "
#| "is an account for an institution you have already created, you can select "
#| "the institution from the dropdown list. If you want to create a new "
#| "institution, click on the <guibutton>New Institution</guibutton> button. "
